select current word, select next in multiselection  ..... ctrl + d
show shortcuts list ...... Ctrl +Shift+P
select current line  ......... ctrl + I
move current line up DOWN ..... alt + UP/DOWN ARROW
copy line up/down  ...  alt + shift + up/down
save all files ... strg+K, danach S
close all opened tabs ... strg+K, danach W

